      "fn_code": "int\nget_accex()\n{\n    int fexc, accx;\n\n    fexc = fetestexcept (FE_ALL_EXCEPT);\n    accx = 0;\n    if (fexc & FE_INEXACT)\n        accx |= 1;\n    if (fexc & FE_DIVBYZERO)\n        accx |= 2;\n    if (fexc & FE_UNDERFLOW)\n        accx |= 4;\n    if (fexc & FE_OVERFLOW)\n        accx |= 8;\n    if (fexc & FE_INVALID)\n        accx |= 0x10;\n    return accx;\n}",
